<h2>Payment Status Update</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>We wanted to inform you about the status of your recent payment related to your order <strong>#{{orderNumber}}</strong>.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Payment Status:</strong> {{paymentStatus}}</li>
  <li><strong>Amount:</strong> KES {{amount}}</li>
  <li><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</li>
  <li><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</li>
  <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{paymentDate}}</li>
</ul>

{{#if isSuccessful}}
  <p>Your payment was successful. We're now processing your order and will notify you once it's shipped.</p>
{{else}}
  <p>Unfortunately, your payment was <strong>{{paymentStatus}}</strong>. Please retry the payment or contact support for assistance.</p>
{{/if}}

<p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>

<p>Thank you for choosing KickKart!</p>

